column5: Looking to get out in the canoe on wednesday for pike. Does anyone know if the ice is off Crowe lake yet? thanks.

Looks like there is still some ice out there, but there is some open water as well. Take a look here:  http://coastwatch.glerl.noaa.gov/modis/modis.cgi/modis?region=o&page=1&template=sub&image=a1.11099.1822.LakeOntario.143.250m.jpg  S.
